(6, 67, 'Master Suites', 'master-suites', '<img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/headers/title-bg-master-suites.svg\" alt=\"\">\n<h2>Brief</h2>\n<div>\n\n    \n<h3>Last Revised</h3>\n\n\n\n\n</div>\n<div><p class=\"uk-text-lead\">We would like two “his &amp; hers” master suites. These rooms should have enough space so as to not feel tight or constricted but they do not need to be excessively or extravagantly large. These rooms are a priority for us and we will sacrifice other elements or requirements in order to get these rooms right.</p>\n<p>We would like the two rooms to share a large ensuite but each with a separate WIR. However, we would also consider a shared WIR, individual ensuites or even two ensuites and two WIRs but we are mindful of the additional expense of duplicating bathrooms.</p>\n<p>If possible, for privacy and noise considerations, the master suites should not adjoin the secondary bedrooms.</p></div>\n<div>\n\n        <h3><i>Note</i></h3>\n    \n        <div><p><i>The images in the gallery on this page illustrate features and elements of interest and do not necessarily represent the overall design style we are wanting to achieve.</i></p></div>\n    \n</div>\n<h2>Essential</h2>\n<ul>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>2 x master suites</div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>As large as is practical within the limitations of the design and available space</div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Abundant natural light and ventilation</div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Air conditioned</div>\n\n    </li>\n    </ul>\n<h2>Highly Desirable</h2>\n<ul>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div><p class=\"uk-margin-remove\">Large enough to comfortably fit:</p>\n<ul class=\"uk-margin-remove\">\n<li>King bed</li>\n<li>2 x night tables</li>\n<li>Armchair</li>\n</ul></div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div><p>Each suite with a WIR</p></div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Ceiling fan in each suite</div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div><p class=\"uk-margin-remove\">Shared “Jack &amp; Jill” ensuite bathroom with access from each suite</p>\n<ul class=\"uk-margin-remove\">\n<li>No bath</li>\n<li>Toilet with a concealed cistern</li>\n<li>Doorless shower</li>\n<li>No glass in shower if practical. If glass is used, it should be frameless</li>\n<li>Long vanity unit with double sink (or one long sink with two tap sets) and large drawers/cupboards</li>\n<li>GPOs at both ends of vanity unit</li>\n<li>Rain showerhead + shower rail</li>\n<li>Large niche or ledge in shower for shampoo etc</li>\n<li>Concealed drains - no unsightly grates. Linear drain in shower?</li>\n<li>Abundant natural light and ventilation</li>\n<li>Window in shower</li>\n<li>Separate his &amp; hers towel rails</li>\n<li>Skylight(s)</li>\n<li>Lockable doors to each suite</li>\n</ul></div>\n\n    </li>\n    </ul>\n<h2>Desirable</h2>\n<ul>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Shared balcony, verandah or breezeway connecting each suite</div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Shared WIR with access from each suite</div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div><p>A gas or ethanol fireplace and space for a wall mounted TV in one of the suites</p></div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Ensuite bathrooms adjoining each suite (no bath & single sink)</div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Window adjacent to toilet (not essential it opens)</div>\n\n    </li>\n    </ul>\n<h2>Impressions</h2>\n<ul>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/bedroom/315ww50.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>315 Ww 50</h3>\n\n\n<div><p>Love this. Simple yet elegant good sized room with \"secret\" panel doors that access the WIR and ensuite. Very nice.</p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/bedroom/contemporary-bedroom-ideas-inspiration-10.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Contemporary Bedroom Ideas Inspiration 10</h3>\n\n\n<div><p><span>Good natural light and v</span>ery stylish mid-century modern aesthetic. Like the floating bed and the windows looking out onto a green roof.</p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/bedroom/contemporary-bedroom-ideas-inspiration-11.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Contemporary Bedroom Ideas Inspiration 11</h3>\n\n\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/bedroom/modern-master-bedroom-image-sept112018-09-10-at-1.28.36-PM-2.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Modern Master Bedroom Image Sept 112018 09 10 At 1 28 36 PM 2</h3>\n\n\n<div><p>Would like to include a fireplace and a wall mounted TV in one of the suites.</p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/bedroom/modern-master-bedroom-image-sept112018-09-10-at-1.28.36-PM-11.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Modern Master Bedroom Image Sept 112018 09 10 At 1 28 36 PM 11</h3>\n\n\n<div><p>Light, bright simple space. Like that the bedroom has direct access to outside.</p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/bedroom/modern-master-bedroom-jan17-00005.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Modern Master Bedroom Jan 17 00005</h3>\n\n\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/bedroom/modern-master-bedroom-jan17-00008.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Modern Master Bedroom Jan 17 00008</h3>\n\n\n<div><p>Small but functional</p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/bedroom/two-story-4-bedroom-modern-home-primary-bedroom-feb252021-min.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Two Story 4 Bedroom Modern Home Primary Bedroom Feb 252021 Min</h3>\n\n\n<div><p>Like the fireplace with TV unit above, large windows with good natural light, ceiling fan and direct access to outside.</p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n    </ul>\n<ul>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/ensuite/241w16.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>241 W 16</h3>\n\n\n<div><p>Like the natural light in the shower</p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/ensuite/256w7.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>256 W 7</h3>\n\n\n<div><p>Plenty of natural light in the shower</p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/ensuite/270w7.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>270 W 7</h3>\n\n\n<div><p>Good natural light in the shower. Like the doorless design with a pony wall separating the shower from the rest of the bathroom</p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/ensuite/411wq6.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>411 Wq 6</h3>\n\n\n<div><p><span>Love the full height windows and frameless glass in the shower</span></p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/ensuite/04-walk-in-shower-ideas-decorsnob-1024x684.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>04 Walk In Shower Ideas Decorsnob 1024 X 684</h3>\n\n\n<div><p>Single glass wall, double entry</p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/ensuite/05-walk-in-shower-ideas-decorsnob.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>05 Walk In Shower Ideas Decorsnob</h3>\n\n\n<div><p>Like having a window in the show, no doors and 3 shower heads allow 2 people to shower at the same time</p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/ensuite/10-walk-in-shower-ideas-decorsnob.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>10 Walk In Shower Ideas Decorsnob</h3>\n\n\n<div><p>Like the bold use of colour as a feature and pony walls separating the shower from the rest of the bathroom</p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/ensuite/13-walk-in-shower-ideas-decorsnob-1024x791.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>13 Walk In Shower Ideas Decorsnob 1024 X 791</h3>\n\n\n<div><p>Like the shower area is on the reverse of a central wall. Don\'t want a bath in the ensuite but a vanity would be well placed in this position instead</p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/ensuite/32-walk-in-shower-ideas-decorsnob.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>32 Walk In Shower Ideas Decorsnob</h3>\n\n\n<div><p>Love the use of concrete and the window. Like the idea of having a bench in the shower area but not convonced wood would wear well in such a wet and humid environment.</p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/ensuite/39-walk-in-shower-ideas-decorsnob.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>39 Walk In Shower Ideas Decorsnob</h3>\n\n\n<div><p>Like the skylight over the shower area, large niche and long vanity with double sink and big drawers</p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/ensuite/44-walk-in-shower-ideas-decorsnob.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>44 Walk In Shower Ideas Decorsnob</h3>\n\n\n<div><p><span>Like the double entry and minimal use of (frameless) glass</span></p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/ensuite/049e73a452e26e533caafdebc6d0843f.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>049 E 73 A 452 E 26 E 533 Caafdebc 6 D 0843 F</h3>\n\n\n<div><p>Like the concrete and interesting skylight</p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/ensuite/1615346577445_16112025382435.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>1615346577445 16112025382435</h3>\n\n\n<div><p>Love the aggregate floor, long shelf in the shower and great natural light</p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/ensuite/1615350382696_1603689494849BULLECOURTMOSMAN19571.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>1615350382696 1603689494849 BULLECOURTMOSMAN 19571</h3>\n\n\n<div><p>Love the dual shower heads and skylight over the shower area</p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/ensuite/1641443324811_bathroom-bathtub.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>1641443324811 Bathroom Bathtub</h3>\n\n\n<div><p>Good natural light over the vanity area. Love the large shower area with dual shower heads and no doors or glass</p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/ensuite/1643766599883_2-Ensuite.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>1643766599883 2 Ensuite</h3>\n\n\n<div><p>Like the good natural light from the window and skylight</p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/ensuite/betonowa-%C5%82azienka-mikrocement05.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Betonowa Lazienka Mikrocement 05</h3>\n\n\n<div><p>Love the thick, heavy-set concrete bench and integrated sink.</p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/ensuite/betonowa-%C5%82azienka-mikrocement06.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Betonowa Lazienka Mikrocement 06</h3>\n\n\n<div><p>Like the use of concrete and the doorless shower. Good natural light from the large window</p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/ensuite/Concrete-Bathroom-Designs-02-1-Kindesign.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Concrete Bathroom Designs 02 1 Kindesign</h3>\n\n\n<div><p>Like the use of concrete and interesting full length skylight. Wouldn\'t want a timber floor in a bathroom at all though</p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/ensuite/Concrete-Bathroom-Designs-10-1-Kindesign.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Concrete Bathroom Designs 10 1 Kindesign</h3>\n\n\n<div><p>Love the concrete bench with dual integrated sinks. Recessing the vanity into the wall is interesting</p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/ensuite/Concrete-Bathroom-Designs-12-1-Kindesign.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Concrete Bathroom Designs 12 1 Kindesign</h3>\n\n\n<div><p>Love the concrete, especially the large heavy-set bench and integrated sink. Great natural light in the shower area</p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/ensuite/Concrete-Bathroom-Designs-14-1-Kindesign.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Concrete Bathroom Designs 14 1 Kindesign</h3>\n\n\n<div><p>Like the use of concrete, the large skylight over the shower and the ledge seat with shower overhead</p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/ensuite/Concrete-Bathroom-Designs-16-1-Kindesign.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Concrete Bathroom Designs 16 1 Kindesign</h3>\n\n\n<div><p>Love the large skylight, big windows, concrete bench with twin sinks, dual shower heads and large shower niche. Don\'t like the timber floor in the shower</p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/ensuite/Concrete-Bathroom-Designs-19-1-Kindesign.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Concrete Bathroom Designs 19 1 Kindesign</h3>\n\n\n<div><p>Like the skylight placed directly over the large concrete vanity</p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/ensuite/shower-seat-01.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Shower Seat 01</h3>\n\n\n<div><p>Like the idea of a bench or seat in the shower area. Nice to be able to sit under the falling water. Would come in handy as we age too no doubt.</p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/ensuite/shower-seat-02.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Shower Seat 02</h3>\n\n\n<div><p><span>Like the idea of a bench or seat in the shower area. Nice to be able to sit under the falling water. </span><span>Would</span><span> come in handy</span><span> as we age too no doubt.</span></p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/ensuite/shower-seat-03.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Shower Seat 03</h3>\n\n\n<div><p><span>Like the idea of a bench or seat in the shower area. Nice to be able to sit under the falling water. </span><span>Would</span><span> come in handy</span><span> as we age too no doubt.</span></p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/ensuite/shower-seat-04.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Shower Seat 04</h3>\n\n\n<div><p><span>Like the idea of a bench or seat in the shower area. Nice to be able to sit under the falling water. </span><span>Would</span><span> come in handy</span><span> as we age too no doubt.</span></p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/ensuite/shower-seat-05.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Shower Seat 05</h3>\n\n\n<div><p><span>Like the idea of a bench or seat in the shower area. Nice to be able to sit under the falling water. </span><span>Would</span><span> come in handy</span><span> as we age too no doubt.</span></p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/ensuite/shower-seat-06.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Shower Seat 06</h3>\n\n\n<div><p><span>Like the idea of a bench or seat in the shower area. Nice to be able to sit under the falling water. </span><span>Would</span><span> come in handy</span><span> as we age too no doubt.</span></p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/ensuite/Shower_Ledge_design_sky_window.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Shower Ledge Design Sky Window</h3>\n\n\n<div><p>Like the large skylight in the shower and use of a ledge (instead of a niche)</p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/ensuite/stanford-university-klopf-architecture-mid-century-home_dezeen.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Stanford University Klopf Architecture Mid Century Home Dezeen</h3>\n\n\n<div><p>Good natural light and large niche in the doorless shower</p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/ensuite/straw-bale-house-sarah-wigglesworth-refurb-architecture-uk_dezeen.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Straw Bale House Sarah Wigglesworth Refurb Architecture Uk Dezeen</h3>\n\n\n<div><p>Like the doorless design of the shower. Don\'t like the dingy lighting</p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/ensuite/zip-litibu-palma-house-mexico_dezeen_1704_col_9.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Zip Litibu Palma House Mexico Dezeen 1704 Col 9</h3>\n\n\n<div><p>Like the use of concrete and the large external door providing natural light</p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/ensuite/412n20.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>412 N 20</h3>\n\n\n<div><p><i>LOVE</i> the shower opening up onto a private outdoor space</p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/ensuite/483w25.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>483 W 25</h3>\n\n\n<div><p>Good natural light in the shower. Like the use of a central wall with the shower on the reverse side of the sinks</p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/ensuite/529w20.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>529 W 20</h3>\n\n\n<div><p>Good natural light and ventilation in the shower</p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/ensuite/570w32.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>570 W 32</h3>\n\n\n<div><p>Like the good light and ventilation from the large windows and louvres</p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/ensuite/570W34.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>570 W 34</h3>\n\n\n<div><p>Like the natural light and ventilation also the doorless shower with frameless glass</p></div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/master-suites/gallery/ensuite/2017553212_9_1_220127_075033-w1600-h1067.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>2017553212 9 1 220127 075033 W 1600 H 1067</h3>\n\n\n<div>Like the large long single sink with twin taps. Also like the marble finish.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n    </ul>\n<p>\n    <a href=\"index.php?Itemid=114\">Living</a>\n</p>\n<p>\n    <a href=\"index.php?Itemid=116\">Bedrooms</a>\n</p>\n', '<!-- {\"type\":\"layout\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"section\",\"props\":{\"style\":\"default\",\"width\":\"\",\"vertical_align\":\"middle\",\"title_position\":\"top-left\",\"title_rotation\":\"left\",\"title_breakpoint\":\"xl\",\"image_position\":\"center-center\",\"image\":\"\",\"animation\":\"fade\",\"preserve_color\":false,\"image_effect\":\"fixed\",\"image_parallax_bgx_start\":\"-300\",\"image_parallax_bgx_end\":\"0\",\"animation_delay\":\"\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"row\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"column\",\"props\":{\"image_position\":\"center-center\",\"media_overlay_gradient\":\"\",\"v