(11, 72, 'Garage', 'garage', '<img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/headers/title-bg-garage.svg\" alt=\"\">\n<h2>Brief</h2>\n<div>\n\n    \n<h3>Last Revised</h3>\n\n\n\n\n</div>\n<div><p class=\"uk-text-lead\">We have two cars and a large motorbike and want to be able to fit them in the garage comfortably.</p>\n<p>Some of the homes within the estate have a <a href=\"#modal-minigarage\" uk-toggle=\"\">small additional “mini” garage with its own roller door</a> situated as an annex on the side of the main garage which is used to store a golf cart. This could be used for the motorbike and would add appeal as a feature prospective buyers are wanting in homes when looking to buy within the estate.</p>\n<p>We would like enough room to be able to store tools out of sight in cupboards and have a workbench if possible.</p>\n<!-- This is the modal -->\n<div id=\"modal-minigarage\" class=\"uk-flex-top\" uk-modal=\"\">\n<div class=\"uk-modal-dialog uk-modal-body uk-margin-auto-vertical\"><img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/brief/garage/18-Kooindah-Boulevard.webp\" />\n<p class=\"uk-text-justify\">Some homes within the Kooindah Waters estate have a small annex attached to the main garage which is used to store a golf cart. We would like something similar but will use it for our motorbike.</p>\n<p class=\"uk-text-justify\">The house at <a href=\"https://www.domain.com.au/18-kooindah-boulevard-wyong-nsw-2259-2017620451\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">18 Kooindah Boulevard</a> demonstrates this feature.</p>\n</div>\n</div></div>\n<h2>Essential</h2>\n<ul>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Enough width to comfortably fit two medium sized SUVs</div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Single garage door</div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Internal access</div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Good lighting</div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Light switch at each entry point, including near the roller door control unit</div>\n\n    </li>\n    </ul>\n<h2>Highly Desirable</h2>\n<ul>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Enough depth to be able to walk around vehicles with the garage door closed</div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Additional annex with separate entry to store motorbike or golf cart - minimum 2m x 3m</div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Polyurethane membrane or sealed polished concrete to garage floor</div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div><p>Space for storage cupboards or racking</p></div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>External access</div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Workbench</div>\n\n    </li>\n    </ul>\n<h2>Desirable</h2>\n<ul>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Loft or mezzanine storage</div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Laundry sink and cabinet unit</div>\n\n    </li>\n    </ul>\n<p>\n    <a href=\"index.php?Itemid=119\">Office</a>\n</p>\n<p>\n    <a href=\"index.php?Itemid=121\">Outdoor Living</a>\n</p>\n', '<!-- {\"name\":\"Page - Brief - v3\",\"type\":\"layout\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"section\",\"props\":{\"style\":\"default\",\"width\":\"\",\"vertical_align\":\"middle\",\"title_position\":\"top-left\",\"title_rotation\":\"left\",\"title_breakpoint\":\"xl\",\"image_position\":\"center-center\",\"image\":\"\",\"animation\":\"fade\",\"preserve_color\":false,\"image_effect\":\"fixed\",\"image_parallax_bgx_start\":\"-300\",\"image_parallax_bgx_end\":\"0\",\"animation_delay\":\"\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"row\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"column\",\"props\":{\"image_position\":\"center-center\",\"media_overlay_gradient\":\"\",\"vertical_align\":\"middle\",\"position_sticky_breakpoint\":\"m\",\"position_sticky\":false},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"image\",\"props\":{\"margin\":\"small\",\"image_svg_color\":\"\",\"image\":\"images\\/headers\\/title-bg-garage.svg\",\"image_svg_inline\":false,\"text_align\":\"center\",\"image_svg_animate\":false}}]}],\"props\":{\"margin\":\"remove-vertical