(16, 79, 'Materials', 'materials', '<img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/headers/title-bg-materials.svg\" alt=\"\">\n<h2>Likes</h2>\n<ul>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Concrete - rough/textured, polished, coloured, decorative aggregate</div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Stone cladding - particularly sandstone</div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Timber - polished, weathered</div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Glass - frameless</div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Steel - stainless, aged/distressed (rusted, weathered), corrugated</div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Metal cladding - zinc, aluminium, steel</div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Contrasting materials</div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Materials used in unusual or unexpected contexts</div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Plants integrated into the aesthetic of the building - green walls/roof</div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Wallpaper - particularly textured</div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Earthy colours, deep rich colours</div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Pastel colours that reflect mid-century hues</div>\n\n    </li>\n    </ul>\n<h2>Dislikes</h2>\n<ul>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Large expanses of Gyprock</div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Cheap, low grade materials, fixtures and fittings that don\'t last, don\'t wear well or damage or corrode easily e.g. flimsy aluminium windows, poor quality lights, soft timbers such as pinewood</div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Grout between tiles used in high traffic or hard wearing areas such as floors/showers. It’s unsightly, a dirt magnet and is impossible to keep clean</div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Poor lighting design or harsh lighting</div>\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        \n<div>Skirting boards</div>\n\n    </li>\n    </ul>\n<h2>Impressions</h2>\n<div>\n\n        <h3><i>Note</i></h3>\n    \n        <div><p><i>The images in the gallery on this page illustrate features and elements of interest and do not necessarily represent the overall design style we are wanting to achieve.</i></p></div>\n    \n</div>\n<ul>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/4.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>4</h3>\n\n\n<div>Like the polished concrete floors. They look good, and are hard wearing. Here the flow from inside to outdoor spaces is enhanced by the use of the concrete floor which extends from inside to out.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/9+-+Luda+Studios_Castle+Cove_Cam_9_Hero-External_High_Res_Final.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>9 Luda Studios Castle Cove Cam 9 Hero External High Res Final</h3>\n\n\n<div>Love buildings that incorporate vegetation into the aesthetic. Plants provide visual interest and appeal, can help to soften hard edges and can deliver positive insulating and environmental outcomes.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/287+Elizabeth+1.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>287 Elizabeth 1</h3>\n\n\n<div>Like the use of stone, particularly sandstone.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/2734fe78f41f2978af6d4ebc027bd5a4.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>2734 Fe 78 F 41 F 2978 Af 6 D 4 Ebc 027 Bd 5 A 4</h3>\n\n\n<div>Like the use of concrete.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/9265a7bb516c3ccfe0ea6f1d12da7d2d.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>9265 A 7 Bb 516 C 3 Ccfe 0 Ea 6 F 1 D 12 Da 7 D 2 D</h3>\n\n\n<div>Love buildings that incorporate vegetation into the aesthetic. Plants provide visual interest and appeal, can help to soften hard edges and can deliver positive insulating and environmental outcomes.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/9171375e3330eb05351dfdbf21a383a4.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>9171375 E 3330 Eb 05351 Dfdbf 21 A 383 A 4</h3>\n\n\n<div>Like the use of weathered steel.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/31655861621_42b3a0dd2e_k.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>31655861621 42 B 3 A 0 Dd 2 E K</h3>\n\n\n<div>Like the mixed use of contrasting materials, colours and textures.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/Anna_Ritsch.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Anna Ritsch</h3>\n\n\n<div>Like the use of concrete and the contrast with the blond timber colour. Love the benches reflecting the concrete used in the floor.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/BAY+STREET+HOUSE+MOSMAN+light+brown+random+square+rockfaced+cladding+curved+walling+artistry+in+stone+%287%29.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>BAY STREET HOUSE MOSMAN Light Brown Random Square Rockfaced Cladding Curved Walling Artistry In Stone 7</h3>\n\n\n<div>Like the mix of materials and textures. Even within the use of sandstone, there is contrast between the smooth floor tiles and the rough finish of the sandstone wall cladding.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/Black-Beauty-Tierra-Villa-in-Costa-Rica.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Black Beauty Tierra Villa In Costa Rica</h3>\n\n\n<div>Love buildings that incorporate vegetation into the aesthetic. Plants provide visual interest and appeal, can help to soften hard edges and can deliver positive insulating and environmental outcomes.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/bluff-house-entry-auhaus-architecture-img_775153ac038936fe_9-0804-1-550035c.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Bluff House Entry Auhaus Architecture Img 775153 Ac 038936 Fe 9 0804 1 550035 C</h3>\n\n\n<div>Weathered steel, concrete and timber. Love the combination here.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/CHAP-2-exterior.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>CHAP 2 Exterior</h3>\n\n\n<div>Like the rich timber cladding.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/Corben_The-Grove_0004_RT-revised.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Corben The Grove 0004 RT Revised</h3>\n\n\n<div>Like the mixed use of materials and integration of vegetation into the aesthetic.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/DAN_Gibbon-Street-house_11.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>DAN Gibbon Street House 11</h3>\n\n\n<div>Love this combination of rusted steel, brick and vegetation.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/e1d469954df4329c127af7901bca033f.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>E 1 D 469954 Df 4329 C 127 Af 7901 Bca 033 F</h3>\n\n\n<div>Love buildings that incorporate vegetation into the aesthetic. Plants provide visual interest and appeal, can help to soften hard edges and can deliver positive insulating and environmental outcomes. In this instance, the house is almost invisible in the landscape.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/feat-1.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Feat 1</h3>\n\n\n<div>Love buildings that incorporate vegetation into the aesthetic. Plants provide visual interest and appeal, can help to soften hard edges and can deliver positive insulating and environmental outcomes.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/feature-project-oak-house-eco-outdoor-aus-img_b261cb080dce1c0f_14-0494-1-2d822f9.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Feature Project Oak House Eco Outdoor Aus Img B 261 Cb 080 Dce 1 C 0 F 14 0494 1 2 D 822 F 9</h3>\n\n\n<div>Love the contrasting materials and finishes and the planted roof.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/foxground-house-louise-nettleton-architects-img_0651bb8003d88870_9-3144-1-314f5ed.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Foxground House Louise Nettleton Architects Img 0651 Bb 8003 D 88870 9 3144 1 314 F 5 Ed</h3>\n\n\n<div>Like the use of corrugated steel as cladding.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/full-metal-jacket-sanctum-design-img_7381c8ed0269b83f_14-8192-1-1fc729d.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Full Metal Jacket Sanctum Design Img 7381 C 8 Ed 0269 B 83 F 14 8192 1 1 Fc 729 D</h3>\n\n\n<div>Love the cladding.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/g8880.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>G 8880</h3>\n\n\n<div>This is fantsastic! Concrete, brick, steel and glass all combined with some wonderful landscape design. Love the grass cascading down to street level like a living river. There\'s even boulders in the stream!</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/garcias-house-warm-architects-concrete-interiors-dezeen-col.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Garcias House Warm Architects Concrete Interiors Dezeen Col</h3>\n\n\n<div>Like the continuation of the concrete floor into the stairs.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/glo-eco-home-green-roof-05_3-2.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Glo Eco Home Green Roof 05 3 2</h3>\n\n\n<div>Love buildings that incorporate vegetation into the aesthetic. Plants provide visual interest and appeal, can help to soften hard edges and can deliver positive insulating and environmental outcomes.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/gosford-quarries-sandstone-suppliers-sandstone-2011-HIA-Home-Year-Mt-White-Brown-Range-Gang-Sawn-Cladding.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Gosford Quarries Sandstone Suppliers Sandstone 2011 HIA Home Year Mt White Brown Range Gang Sawn Cladding</h3>\n\n\n<div>Really like the sandstone cladding.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/hill-house-mihaly-slocombe-img_a7d1b56900ee3b8a_9-2918-1-3a11456.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Hill House Mihaly Slocombe Img A 7 D 1 B 56900 Ee 3 B 8 A 9 2918 1 3 A 11456</h3>\n\n\n<div>Like the use of corrugated steel.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/Image-2.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Image 2</h3>\n\n\n<div>Really like this used of mixed materials, steel (aluminium?) cladding, timber and sandstone. Love how the hard box shapes have been softened through the use of vegetation.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/IMG_5980-Edit.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>IMG 5980 Edit</h3>\n\n\n<div>What a fantastic rooftop garden!</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/large.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Large</h3>\n\n\n<div>Love this - especially the upstairs balcony that takes advantage of the greened roof. Also like the sliding adjustable louvres that provide privacy and climate control.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/manning-road-house-noxon-giffen-img_f31153e80403cf1d_9-3026-1-05fa772.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Manning Road House Noxon Giffen Img F 31153 E 80403 Cf 1 D 9 3026 1 05 Fa 772</h3>\n\n\n<div>Like this combination of timber and steel cladding.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/MatthewWoodwardArchitecture_WallisLakeHouse_000004.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Matthew Woodward Architecture Wallis Lake House 000004</h3>\n\n\n<div>Love the use of concrete. Love the use of vegetation.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/2016546761_13_1_201012_120310-w2392-h1062.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>2016546761 13 1 201012 120310 W 2392 H 1062</h3>\n\n\n<div>Absolutely love this. So many elements and materials that appeal - the brutal concrete, the weathered timber, large openings and plants integrated into the home\'s form.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/splash+back+tile+outset_design+Medium+Brown+Sawn+Cladding.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Splash Back Tile Outset Design Medium Brown Sawn Cladding</h3>\n\n\n<div>Interesting use of sandstone as a splashback in the kitchen. Like when matrials are used in unusual or unexpected contexts.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/Mid-Century-Modern-10.-Matt-Gibson.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Mid Century Modern 10 Matt Gibson</h3>\n\n\n<div>Really like the mid-century modern style and the use of timber materials.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/MLF21_Woodwood_CarlottaSt_00067-arnold-standard-thumb-medium-1000x989.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>MLF 21 Woodwood Carlotta St 00067 Arnold Standard Thumb Medium 1000 X 989</h3>\n\n\n<div>Steel, concrete, timber and glass... love it all. Really like the planted awning too!</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/Nha-Trang-house-by-VTN-lead.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Nha Trang House By VTN Lead</h3>\n\n\n<div>A terraced roof garden!</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/NorthcoteResidence02-feature.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Northcote Residence 02 Feature</h3>\n\n\n<div>Love polished concrete floors.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/polished-concrete-brisbane-ozgrind-kitchen-home.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Polished Concrete Brisbane Ozgrind Kitchen Home</h3>\n\n\n<div>Love polished concrete floors.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/riverside-dr-house-lachlan-shepherd-architects-img_aed1109c0580ad0a_9-6013-1-45d0dfd.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Riverside Dr House Lachlan Shepherd Architects Img Aed 1109 C 0580 Ad 0 A 9 6013 1 45 D 0 Dfd</h3>\n\n\n<div>Nice mix of materials.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/maxresdefault.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Maxresdefault</h3>\n\n\n<div>Love the industrial look of the concrete rendered brick. The succulent themed landscaping compliments this very well.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/south-coast-house-acacia-joinery-pty-ltd-img_7611609904e68594_9-1713-1-3baa513.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>South Coast House Acacia Joinery Pty Ltd Img 7611609904 E 68594 9 1713 1 3 Baa 513</h3>\n\n\n<div>Like the weathered steel cladding and oversized eaves.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/MatthewWoodwardArchitecture_WallisLakeHouse_000043.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Matthew Woodward Architecture Wallis Lake House 000043</h3>\n\n\n<div>One wing is timber, the other is concrete. Great effective mix of materials. Particularly like the plants cascading over the roofline. Love the retractable screens on the upstairs balcony as well.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/SWR-1-ext.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>SWR 1 Ext</h3>\n\n\n<div>Lovely combination of materials.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/8546.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>8546</h3>\n\n\n<div>Love the use of the dark timber cladding. This will only look better with age.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/2016546761_4_1_201012_120310-w2392-h1062.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>2016546761 4 1 201012 120310 W 2392 H 1062</h3>\n\n\n<div>Love how plants have been used here to soften the brutalist form of the concrete.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/86462-FACADESOLARPANE-MichaelLassman.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>86462 FACADESOLARPANE Michael Lassman</h3>\n\n\n<div>Love a rooftop garden!</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/86469-LOVRESSOLARPANE-MurrayFredericks.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>86469 LOVRESSOLARPANE Murray Fredericks</h3>\n\n\n<div>Great mix of materials, textures and colour in this fascade.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/86495-ANGLEDEXTERIORN-MurrayFredericks.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>86495 ANGLEDEXTERIORN Murray Fredericks</h3>\n\n\n<div>Love the eclectic mix of materials and the rooftop garden.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/2017151953_17_1_210723_070236-w1600-h1200.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>2017151953 17 1 210723 070236 W 1600 H 1200</h3>\n\n\n<div>Like the mix of different cladding materials.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/2017151953_19_1_210723_070236-w1600-h1200.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>2017151953 19 1 210723 070236 W 1600 H 1200</h3>\n\n\n<div>Love the snadstone paving. Really like the how the roofline has been softened with the use of plants.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/2017195967_2_1_211110_050755-w4000-h2668.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>2017195967 2 1 211110 050755 W 4000 H 2668</h3>\n\n\n<div>Love the steel and stone cladding and timber decking designed to silver with age. Also like the concrete retaining wall.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/Bedroom_Window_-_CaseyDunn.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>Bedroom Window Casey Dunn</h3>\n\n\n<div>Like the steel, glass and concrete. Also really like the use of gabion cages to form privacy screens/walls.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n        <li>\n\n        <img src=\"/2-birdie-place/images/pages/materials/gallery/WELCOME-TO-THE-JUNGLE-HOUSE_EXTERIOR-FRONT-DAY-VIEW-3-822x1030.webp\" alt=\"\">\n\n\n<h3>WELCOME TO THE JUNGLE HOUSE EXTERIOR FRONT DAY VIEW 3 822 X 1030</h3>\n\n\n<div>Love plants incorporated into the design aesthetic of a building.</div>\n\n\n    </li>\n    </ul>\n<p>\n    <a href=\"index.php?Itemid=108\">Specifications</a>\n</p>\n<p>\n    <a href=\"index.php?Itemid=112\">Kitchen</a>\n</p>\n', '<!-- {\"name\":\"Concept\",\"type\":\"layout\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"section\",\"props\":{\"style\":\"default\",\"width\":\"\",\"vertical_align\":\"middle\",\"title_position\":\"top-left\",\"title_rotation\":\"left\",\"title_breakpoint\":\"xl\",\"image_position\":\"center-center\",\"image\":\"\",\"animation\":\"fade\",\"preserve_color\":false,\"image_effect\":\"fixed\",\"image_parallax_bgx_start\":\"-300\",\"image_parallax_bgx_end\":\"0\",\"animation_delay\":\"\"},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"row\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"column\",\"props\":{\"image_position\":\"center-center\",\"media_overlay_gradient\":\"\",\"vertical_align\":\"middle\",\"position_sticky_breakpoint\":\"m\",\"position_sticky\":false},\"children\":[{\"type\":\"image\",\"props\":{\"margin\":\"small\",\"image_svg_color\":\"\",\"image\":\"images\\/headers\\/title-bg-materials.svg\",\"image_svg_inline\":false,\"text_align\":\"cen